s ability to protect. The best way to know objectively how computer security software performs relative to the competition is with reference to objective test results from labs such as AV-Test. Unfortunately, we do not have test results for the Android component of AVG. However, in July and August of 2013, AVG Premium Security participated in two months of ongoing Windows 7 testing in three areas conducted by AV-Test. AVG achieved its highest scores in usability, where it exceled. The usability tests measured how the software affects the usability of the computer in several ways: false warnings about safe URLs, false warnings during system scans about perfectly safe software, and false warnings or false blockages in the process of installing or using software that is actually safe.","AVG turned in good, not excellent, results in tests designed to measure effectiveness at protection. Some tests checked to see how well the software detected brand-new threats for which no signatures already existed. Other tests subjected the software to malware known to exist for the four weeks prior to the tests and measured how well it could detect it. In performance tests to see how AVG influenced the speed of the computer while visiting URLs, downloading software or copying files, performance was adequate but not among the best.","<strong>Help &amp; Support</strong><br/>AVG provides exceptional support: You can receive help via online chat or telephone at all hours. The support site that AVG hosts contains many useful resources, including free virus removal tools listed by name."]},"id":"19d63108-f52d-4c14-bbaf-e85f98821a40","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"9e3c1de4-0402-4152-8931-91ea34d793fe","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["With a single purchase of AVG Premium Security, you have a comprehensive protection suite for your Windows PC that has demonstrated excellent usability, good protection and acceptable performance. You also have a tool that will protect Android devices. Although there are no third-party test results, the Android component of AVG has useful features. For example you can block unwanted calls and messages, and if you ever lose your phone or someone steals it, you can locate it via GPS; you can lock it so nobody can steal your data; or you can wipe it remotely. There are competitive products with better performance and more features, which protect more types of devices."]},"id":"47d3e8e1-2b01-4c22-9f13-e2d4426cfe5c","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_58214","url":"/avg-premium-security-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"nicole-johnston","url":"/author/nicole-johnston","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Nicole Johnston","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"nR6fcTbvfudgncYJbhzqDB","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2013-11-19T15:50:03Z","datePublished":"2013-11-19T15:50:03Z","name":"AVG Premium Security 2014","synopsis":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it is no longer available.","review":{"rating":72,"verdict":"Although AVG Premium Security provides adequate protection for Windows and Android devices, there are competitors who are better at protection and who protect more types of devices. ","pros":["AVG Premium Security produces good protection test results at independent software test labs. "],"cons":["This product is for Windows and Android devices only. "]},"strapline":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it is no longer available.","language":"en","dateModified":"2013-11-19T15:50:03Z","id":"Fg9rNoFbY9EGmNdgcoe8JT","meta":{"title":"AVG Premium Security 2014 Review - Pros, Cons and Verdict","description":"TopTenREVIEWS reviews includes AVG Premium Security in its all-in-one security software reviews."},"products":[{"slug":"avg-premium-security-2014","url":"/product/avg-premium-security-